[thinking] **Considering class loading options**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm looking at how the finalizerLoader's `loadClass` method uses the system parent classloader. If the system has Guice, it seems to work fine, but what if the classpath for build or test is missing? I need to check if it does exist or not. If it doesn't, a URL loader should be able to find it from the base. Just making sure I'm clear on how all of this gets integrated!
