[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering class loading options**\n\nI'm looking at how the finalizerLoader's `loadClass` method uses the system parent classloader. If the system has Guice, it seems to work fine, but what if the classpath for build or test is missing? I need to check if it does exist or not. If it doesn't, a URL loader should be able to find it from the base. Just making sure I'm clear on how all of this gets integrated!\n\n**Evaluating JUnit Order**\n\nI'm thinking about the order of JUnit tests. Could class discovery be deterministic and based on lexicographic order? It did run before the others. I wonder if XML timestamps play a role in this. I feel like I need to read more about other timestamps to clarify what's happening. There's definitely something worth exploring here regarding how the ordering works in JUnit.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0546e149f87d035b0169fa5044b3ac81968566ea6627655e37\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-lBWcz0Z9-NM2byPaN0BfS3aUJMTrrVd4MVA7givvyAwlnC2eFEHWntle_aITt0l9mLNuStG5FSAluB6qWyqIvhgMxdbaCJVx2KEuOtzsrsFMuni7kipWjVVIktqoH5cq9VPQJmbj-4DP8xnpFiHP7Kj5s-Xl98CbFD_nog52WaKhf8_hYRaV26cubMkBQRV9xQadAFU6sH5uYEozDUCqjuMhTbv7On_Td44saQw8sMGxpYquKqun_Bm498acLnA8SFq4c3noDET1cJJTgia6ae9IQOV_o9BGCmIpsgUOYhUT3yDcI5lnXq_HEQq0cEDA-dQtOVrUpcs2zkI_hr6Ye0lzenMnAk_qgxo2vQNvekiT6CVfp2VyVFauxPQ-LRUbrdep7WIkizCrOJhpJty4zAj4G3mtKN7PjcEpfCDws5oUGM6S95S1A8YSkN2Le8LAy0ug3YrIbJDrrJI_f7APjxH9XDu3J9zXtWPhdW19ymZWBEtWQIZlWMLzzh3-pa7-zs-dTvPVcFkmZwwPITiTs8kJ-cLdEoCUo3t3YspkxIU4APNDls4podayMcJVcb974dbzxS3zPa6K3cgd_pCxSNIpE-SzyFl2d6KLvO9rUQFTm7kU17_sgeh-mN8HAIQaeafkCOR8D6qvWpNgpZM_3Cv_5utZ98DpG8Z3QwmAGSD_gdVy39BdkfpKEnRyYDL200ZEdsatM50MkbBAWuEjylBfBH66EZx31Nc10ko9F5wOZFk2jywoORuD2Vr2JoJjgdhL73pIi9Nq7sb3Z9ak1Mw2HzZkiBG2vqDGCuyDWMSDS2treYGJX7ErIfh_VXi7H2M4Mbl8gMJlk9sRyVE0htNXHV94y4z5lTRM_XdtuVfEgsdx7Qt-ptZtmy5zQinbrNDcPvDmOENbniTO00QvX_JGqct1bLX