[assistant] 
[assistant] - Simplified the dedicated active-class test:
[assistant]   - `tests/src/com.google.inject/guice/3.0/src/test/java/com_google_inject/guice/InnerFinalizableReferenceQueueInnerDecoupledLoaderTest.java`
[assistant] 
