[assistant] 
[assistant] - Updated:
[assistant]   - `tests/src/com.google.inject/guice/3.0/build.gradle`
[assistant] 
[assistant]   to package the helper class into a tiny bootclasspath jar and run JVM tests with:
[assistant] 
[assistant]   - `-Djava.system.class.loader=com_google_inject.guice.DenyGuiceFinalizerSystemClassLoader`
[assistant] 
[assistant] This avoids `SecurityManager`, so it should no longer fail on Java versions where setting a security manager is unsupported. I did not run the tests.
